---
title: Carb Smart Sweet Potato and Goat Cheese Salad with Lentils and Pepitas
description: This hearty salad is delicious hot, cold or at room temperature! Rich goat cheese and wholesome lentils pack each bite with meatless protein.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-de-patates-douces-et-de-fromage-de-chevre-4b041a1c-ba9484f4.jpg
